result.name: Franks

reviews.text: Have been back to this place 3 times so far and every time has been great; delicious, hot food with friendly service. Their homemade fried pizza dough served with classic red sauce is amazing and very addictive. Also like that they are able to make cocktails that aren't on their menu.
Frank's does a great job capturing the New York red sauce experience at a reasonable price. Bold flavors and a nice range of items. Cool vibe too.

Everything about this place is awesome. The food (upstairs and at the bar) is fantastic, the kids are amazing and reasonably priced, the music is in point, and the staff are better than all the above! Highly recommended!

Absolutely phenomenal restaurant. From top to bottom one of the best experiences I have ever had. The atmosphere is relaxed and refined. The music is all vinyl spun live. The drinks are wonderfully crafted and delivered with care. The food is absolutely one of a kind and like nothing I have had. I had my doubts going to an Italian restaurant in Hong Kong but have no doubt this is a must visit. 

All of those things still don’t do justice to the best part of the entire place. The staff and the service they provide is better than I have received in any restaurant the world over. The manager, Wahid, floats around the dining room with an eye so keen he doesn’t miss a single detail. He is incredibly engaging and takes time to talk with customers and his recommendations are not to ignored. If he tells you to get something you should not even think twice. His service and level of care shows a true devotion to providing an incredible experience for customers. Me and my friends had the opportunity to meet several of the staff including the head chef and the proprietor and they treated us more live friends than customers. Honestly there are not enough words to describe how incredible the experience was. It’s not a question of if but when I will return to Frank’s. Don’t even hesitate to walk in and dine here. Unbelievably good.
I love this restaurant. People there are very nice and offer great service. Food taste pretty good. I love their drinks!
